---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="VirtualStruct &mdash; Projects" ogTitle="VirtualStruct &mdash; Projects"
  description="Projects by Amara Nezli — open source and professional work." showBack={true}>

  <div class="bento-page">
    <div class="bento-grid">

      <!-- Header row -->
      <div class="bcard bcard-full bcard-nav">
        <span class="bento-page-title">Projects</span>
      </div>

      <!-- Professional work -->
      <div class="bcard bcard-full">
        <span class="bcard-section-title">Professional</span>
        <div class="project-grid">
          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://zirak.info" class="card-title-link">Zirak</a> <span class="badge-private">private src</span></h3>
            <p>Real-time car-sharing platform with WebSocket-based live tracking and booking.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Node.js</span><span>Laravel</span><span>WebSocket</span><span>GCP</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://docminute.app" class="card-title-link">Docminute</a> <span class="badge-private">private src</span></h3>
            <p>On-demand doctor consultation platform.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Laravel</span><span>Node.js</span><span>MySQL</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://heyu.paris" class="card-title-link">HeyU</a> <span class="badge-private">private src</span></h3>
            <p>Social discovery app for events and local experiences in Paris.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Laravel</span><span>Node.js</span><span>AWS</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://sherpas.com" class="card-title-link">Sherpas</a> <span class="badge-private">private src</span></h3>
            <p>Tutoring marketplace. Led the legacy code migration and new feature releases.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Laravel</span><span>MySQL</span><span>Docker</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3>Gratify <span class="badge-private">private</span></h3>
            <p>Rewards and loyalty platform built from scratch.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Laravel</span><span>Node.js</span><span>Redis</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3>Zer <span class="badge-private">private</span></h3>
            <p>Internal operations platform.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Node.js</span><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>Docker</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://dzvolt.com/en/software/dzvolt-ui" class="card-title-link">DzVolt UI</a> <span class="badge-private">private src</span></h3>
            <p>Desktop app for monitoring and controlling industrial I/O over Modbus RTU, with real-time browser streaming, role-based access, and tamper-evident audit logging.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Desktop</span><span>Modbus RTU</span><span>Cross-platform</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Open source -->
      <div class="bcard bcard-full">
        <span class="bcard-section-title">Open Source</span>
        <div class="project-grid">
          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://hihebark.github.io/appwire/" class="card-title-link">Appwire</a></h3>
            <p>Live REPL for inspecting a running app — run code against real service instances.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Node.js</span><span>NestJS</span><span>REPL</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://fanar-app.github.io/" class="card-title-link">Fanar</a></h3>
            <p>Debugging tool that streams objects, errors, SQL queries, and performance metrics from any runtime to a real-time desktop app.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Debugging</span><span>Desktop</span><span>Open Source</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/nestjs-query-profiler" class="card-title-link">nestjs-query-profiler</a></h3>
            <p>NestJS module for profiling database query performance.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>NestJS</span><span>TypeScript</span><span>npm</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/hihebark/QuranReader" class="card-title-link">QuranReader</a></h3>
            <p>Native GNOME application for reading the Quran.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Python</span><span>GTK4</span><span>libadwaita</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/hihebark/blocktheid" class="card-title-link">blocktheid</a></h3>
            <p>Browser extension to block Vercel-hosted websites.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>JavaScript</span><span>Browser</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/hihebark/bevor" class="card-title-link">Bevor</a></h3>
            <p>HTTP request and payload validator.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Go</span><span>Security</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://hihebark.github.io/vimd/" class="card-title-link">Vimd</a></h3>
            <p>In-browser markdown previewer.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>JavaScript</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/hihebark/Duxe" class="card-title-link">Duxe</a></h3>
            <p>Information gathering and reconnaissance tool.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Go</span><span>Security</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/hihebark/godirsearch" class="card-title-link">godirsearch</a></h3>
            <p>Fast directory and path enumeration tool for web targets.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Go</span><span>Security</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/hihebark/horcrux-js" class="card-title-link">Horcrux-js</a></h3>
            <p>Split a file into encrypted shards using Shamir's Secret Sharing.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Node.js</span><span>Cryptography</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/hihebark/dotfiles" class="card-title-link">dotfiles</a></h3>
            <p>Personal shell and editor configuration files.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Shell</span></div>
          </div>

          <div class="exp-entry">
            <h3><a href="https://github.com/hihebark/MyScripts" class="card-title-link">MyScripts</a></h3>
            <p>Collection of utility scripts for day-to-day automation.</p>
            <div class="stack"><span>Shell</span><span>Automation</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
